### Upload dataset
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/datasets/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample_students.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ./sample_students.csv
--boundary--

### List datasets
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/datasets
Accept: application/json

### Import UCI dataset by ID
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/datasets/uci
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "uci_id": 53
}

### Import UCI dataset by name
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/datasets/uci
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Iris"
}

### Preview dataset
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/datasets/PUT_DATASET_ID_HERE?rows=8
Accept: application/json
